1
00:00:04,450 --> 00:00:05,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Isn't this nice?</font>

2
00:00:06,110 --> 00:00:09,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We haven't been on a trip 
since we went camping.</font>

3
00:00:09,610 --> 00:00:10,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes,</font>

4
00:00:10,960 --> 00:00:13,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and it's our first time just 
the two of us...</font>

5
00:00:13,800 --> 00:00:16,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I didn't expect to stumble 
into a hot springs town on our drive.</font>

6
00:00:16,410 --> 00:00:19,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes, it was a good idea to stop by!</font>

7
00:00:20,090 --> 00:00:24,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I don't do hot springs, 
but the footbath is nice.</font>

8
00:00:24,050 --> 00:00:27,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?! You can't do hot springs either?</font>

9
00:00:27,340 --> 00:00:31,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well... I <i>can</i> do them...</font>

10
00:00:39,400 --> 00:00:41,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And down I...</font>

11
00:00:41,840 --> 00:00:42,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey!</font>

12
00:00:44,170 --> 00:00:48,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">At hot springs and public baths, 
I'm at risk of being sat on.</font>

13
00:00:48,780 --> 00:00:50,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's not fun.</font>

14
00:00:50,210 --> 00:00:52,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ah, I see...</font>

15
00:00:52,360 --> 00:00:58,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I can use them if I have help, 
but I always hate to be a bother...</font>

16
00:00:58,620 --> 00:01:00,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I end up thinking, "I can have 
a hot bath at home."</font>

17
00:01:01,160 --> 00:01:04,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I guess hot springs are 
a bridge too far for both of us.</font>

18
00:01:05,820 --> 00:01:12,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But this might also be my first time 
feeling properly healed by a hot spring...</font>

19
00:01:16,070 --> 00:01:18,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes, agreed.</font>

20
00:01:25,560 --> 00:01:27,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Are you ready to head back?</font>

21
00:01:27,010 --> 00:01:30,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I can't wait to eat these 
hot spring eggs at home!</font>

22
00:01:34,050 --> 00:01:37,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sir, please, you can't—</font>

23
00:01:37,400 --> 00:01:39,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I've had enough! I'm leaving!</font>

24
00:01:39,480 --> 00:01:40,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">P-Please, let's talk this out!</font>

25
00:01:40,890 --> 00:01:43,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I knew it wasn't just my imagination!</font>

26
00:01:43,230 --> 00:01:46,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm not staying in this haunted house!</font>

27
00:01:46,730 --> 00:01:48,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}It's not a haunted house!</font>

28
00:01:48,200 --> 00:01:50,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What's that all about?</font>

29
00:01:48,640 --> 00:01:50,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Please, come back!</font>

30
00:01:50,190 --> 00:01:52,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It appears the local inn is haunted.</font>

31
00:01:52,950 --> 00:01:56,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We've been called to investigate 
hauntings from time to time...</font>

32
00:01:56,180 --> 00:01:57,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Have they ever been real?</font>

33
00:01:59,340 --> 00:02:03,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Paranormal activity tends to be 
someone's fears getting out of control,</font>

34
00:02:03,200 --> 00:02:06,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">or the abilities 
of previously undiscovered races.</font>

35
00:02:09,000 --> 00:02:11,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You investigate hauntings?!</font>

36
00:02:20,260 --> 00:02:22,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Do forgive the sudden request.</font>

37
00:02:22,720 --> 00:02:26,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I am the proprietress of this inn,</font>

38
00:02:26,410 --> 00:02:30,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and we've been plagued 
by rumors of a haunting of late!</font>

39
00:02:30,590 --> 00:02:33,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm afraid I'm here 
in a personal capacity...</font>

40
00:02:33,510 --> 00:02:36,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll put you up for free 
while you investigate!</font>

41
00:02:36,940 --> 00:02:39,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">All-inclusive!</font>

42
00:02:39,000 --> 00:02:42,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So please, stay and help me!</font>

43
00:02:40,080 --> 00:02:42,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Th-This was supposed to be 
a day trip, though...</font>

44
00:02:42,940 --> 00:02:46,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're free to visit my 
agency at a later date.</font>

45
00:02:51,880 --> 00:02:55,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But in the meantime, I'll keep 
being swamped by awful reviews!</font>

46
00:02:55,310 --> 00:02:58,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I can't afford to lose more customers!</font>

47
00:02:58,820 --> 00:03:00,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But I'm serious—</font>

48
00:03:00,440 --> 00:03:05,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll rent you my best room,
with an open-air bath!</font>

49
00:03:06,530 --> 00:03:08,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's built on 
universal design principles,</font>

50
00:03:09,220 --> 00:03:12,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">so I guarantee a comfortable stay...</font>

51
00:03:12,390 --> 00:03:14,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{M}A private, open-air bath?</i></font>

52
00:03:17,990 --> 00:03:19,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{M}No one else around!</i></font>

53
00:03:21,260 --> 00:03:24,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm afraid it's just not possible.</font>

54
00:03:24,080 --> 00:03:26,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I have another job to do tomorrow...</font>

55
00:03:27,000 --> 00:03:29,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{M}I can go in by myself...</i></font>

56
00:03:30,930 --> 00:03:34,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Um... I <i>could</i> rearrange our schedule.</font>

57
00:03:35,440 --> 00:03:36,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I think it would be possible.</font>

58
00:03:43,830 --> 00:03:47,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The attendant will show
you to your room!</font>

59
00:03:50,370 --> 00:03:52,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Right this way!</font>

60
00:03:54,750 --> 00:03:57,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{M}The room's set up like this!</i></font>

61
00:03:59,720 --> 00:04:02,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{M}It does have nice scenery...</i></font>

62
00:04:02,550 --> 00:04:05,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{M}But the bath is visible 
from inside the room...</i></font>

63
00:04:05,420 --> 00:04:08,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{M}How am I going to tell Shizuka-san?</i></font>

64
00:04:09,960 --> 00:04:14,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{M}If I just close the curtain 
to block off the view,</i></font>

65
00:04:15,640 --> 00:04:18,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{M}I probably won't need to tell her.</i></font>

66
00:04:19,480 --> 00:04:25,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{M}Maybe this is what she meant 
about me being too accommodating?</i></font>

67
00:04:25,030 --> 00:04:28,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That should be everything. 
Do enjoy your stay!</font>

68
00:04:29,200 --> 00:04:33,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Akira-san, I want to 
get right into the bath!</font>

69
00:04:34,640 --> 00:04:37,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll speak to the proprietress 
about the haunting.</font>

70
00:04:37,360 --> 00:04:39,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Call me if you need any help.</font>

71
00:04:39,380 --> 00:04:40,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Okay!</font>

72
00:04:40,960 --> 00:04:43,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}BATHS ARE ONLY AVAILABLE TO
OVERNIGHT CLIENTS AT THIS TIME</font>

73
00:04:45,140 --> 00:04:47,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You really don't have
any customers, I see.</font>

74
00:04:47,170 --> 00:04:50,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes, it's as bad as it looks.</font>

75
00:04:50,070 --> 00:04:52,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We've had a string of cancellations...</font>

76
00:04:52,270 --> 00:04:53,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}THEY REALLY NEED TO FIX THAT.
IT WAS SCARY, CREEPY, AND I HATED IT!!!</font>

77
00:04:52,590 --> 00:04:55,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I guess it is the reviews.</font>

78
00:04:53,310 --> 00:04:55,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}BLOOD COVERING THE FLOOR?!
TOO FREAKY FOR ME...</font>

79
00:04:55,840 --> 00:04:57,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Blood covering the floor?</font>

80
00:04:58,870 --> 00:05:01,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's certainly an unsettling image...</font>

81
00:05:01,320 --> 00:05:02,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's impossible!</font>

82
00:05:02,950 --> 00:05:05,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'd certainly have noticed 
blood on the floors!</font>

83
00:05:05,390 --> 00:05:09,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes, and they say it 
disappeared right after...</font>

84
00:05:09,070 --> 00:05:11,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Had you heard about this before?</font>

85
00:05:11,450 --> 00:05:17,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A customer once called the front desk
about it in the middle of the night.</font>

86
00:05:18,220 --> 00:05:22,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We went to check later 
and saw nothing of the sort!</font>

87
00:05:22,380 --> 00:05:23,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}SAW A PALE FIGURE AT NIGHT. TOO CREEPY. 
LOVED THE FRESH FOOD, THOUGH.</font>

88
00:05:22,630 --> 00:05:26,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What about the dragging sounds at night?</font>

89
00:05:23,260 --> 00:05:26,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}HEARD DRAGGING SOUNDS DURING THE NIGHT.
WAY TOO CREEPY!</font>

90
00:05:26,170 --> 00:05:31,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You may hear customers' luggage 
 during the day, but never at night!</font>

91
00:05:31,410 --> 00:05:35,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{M}Dragging sounds... Is it related 
to the bloodstained floors?</i></font>

92
00:05:36,190 --> 00:05:39,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What about this "torso ghost"?</font>

93
00:05:36,940 --> 00:05:39,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}SAW A GHOSTLY TORSO FLOATING BY DURING
THE NIGHT. I THINK THE PLACE IS HAUNTED.</font>

94
00:05:39,690 --> 00:05:41,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It seems to appear at night, too.</font>

95
00:05:41,840 --> 00:05:43,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">There's no ghost here!</font>

96
00:05:43,480 --> 00:05:48,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I've worked at this inn for ages, 
and never seen the likes of that!</font>

97
00:05:48,700 --> 00:05:52,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, it's true that not a single 
haunting I've investigated</font>

98
00:05:52,720 --> 00:05:55,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">had a real ghost behind it.</font>

99
00:05:55,770 --> 00:05:59,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">As you can see, 
I'm completely at my wit's end!</font>

100
00:05:59,620 --> 00:06:02,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We had no idea about 
any of this until people</font>

101
00:06:02,520 --> 00:06:05,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">started complaining 
and leaving those reviews!</font>

102
00:06:06,160 --> 00:06:07,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Understood.</font>

103
00:06:08,210 --> 00:06:10,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll continue my investigation, then.</font>

104
00:06:15,810 --> 00:06:19,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{M}No traces of blood 
in the hallway that I can see.</i></font>

105
00:06:20,270 --> 00:06:24,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{M}Was it wiped up immediately after? 
To hide the evidence?</i></font>

106
00:06:28,000 --> 00:06:31,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{M}The only witnesses are guests, 
and it mostly happens late at night.</i></font>

107
00:06:31,650 --> 00:06:36,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{M}The reviews talk about impressions,
 nothing particularly concrete.</i></font>

108
00:06:36,580 --> 00:06:39,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{M}Not nearly enough information 
or evidence to go on.</i></font>

109
00:06:39,660 --> 00:06:43,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{M}I'd have preferred to approach this 
with more time and equipment...</i></font>

110
00:06:45,220 --> 00:06:47,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{M}I can't believe I was bought off 
with an open-air bath.</i></font>

111
00:06:48,040 --> 00:06:51,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{M}If I can't solve it today, 
I'll have to come back another time.</i></font>

112
00:06:53,170 --> 00:06:54,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm back.</font>

113
00:06:56,720 --> 00:06:57,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Akira-san!</font>

114
00:06:57,980 --> 00:07:01,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The attendant helped me into a yukata!</font>

115
00:07:03,330 --> 00:07:07,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{M}Drat. My gratitude is starting 
to overtake my regrets!</i></font>

116
00:07:08,680 --> 00:07:09,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You look beautiful.</font>

117
00:07:09,760 --> 00:07:11,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hooray!</font>

118
00:07:11,660 --> 00:07:13,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The bath was just heavenly.</font>

119
00:07:13,930 --> 00:07:15,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You should try it, too!</font>

120
00:07:15,800 --> 00:07:18,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No, I should get back to work.</font>

121
00:07:20,510 --> 00:07:22,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes, I suppose so.</font>

122
00:07:22,440 --> 00:07:24,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm sorry for getting ahead of myself.</font>

123
00:07:32,690 --> 00:07:36,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This time, you're not going to 
let work take over your personal life.</font>

124
00:07:36,460 --> 00:07:38,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't do it!</font>

125
00:07:42,800 --> 00:07:46,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The reviews suggest the phenomena 
happens mostly at night.</font>

126
00:07:46,260 --> 00:07:48,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It should be fine to wait until then.</font>

127
00:07:51,960 --> 00:07:54,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Isn't this a window?</font>

128
00:07:54,440 --> 00:07:57,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why did Akira-san close the curtains?</font>

129
00:07:57,360 --> 00:08:00,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He's free to enjoy 
the scenery if he wants...</font>

130
00:08:00,730 --> 00:08:03,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Is he accommodating me again?</font>

131
00:08:03,020 --> 00:08:03,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Darn it...</font>

132
00:08:06,110 --> 00:08:08,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Shizuka-san. I'm sorry for the wait.</font>

133
00:08:08,440 --> 00:08:11,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Akira-san, why did you 
close the curtains?!</font>

134
00:08:11,840 --> 00:08:12,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ma'am.</font>

135
00:08:12,750 --> 00:08:17,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Didn't the attendant say the view 
from the room was incredible?!</font>

136
00:08:17,320 --> 00:08:18,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ma'am.</font>

137
00:08:18,110 --> 00:08:20,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Stop worrying about me and just enjoy it!</font>

138
00:08:20,920 --> 00:08:23,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You don't need to be 
accommodating like that!</font>

139
00:08:23,760 --> 00:08:26,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I've brought this on myself, really.</font>

140
00:08:26,570 --> 00:08:27,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?</font>

141
00:08:31,770 --> 00:08:34,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm sorry I didn't tell you.</font>

142
00:08:34,160 --> 00:08:37,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I-It's fine, since I can't see...</font>

143
00:08:37,120 --> 00:08:39,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, I also can't be seen...</font>

144
00:08:39,350 --> 00:08:40,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">B-But...</font>

145
00:08:41,110 --> 00:08:43,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Even if you can't be seen,</font>

146
00:08:43,670 --> 00:08:47,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">you don't like having people look 
into your clothing, right?</font>

147
00:08:47,300 --> 00:08:52,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I was covered in lather, so that 
does lead to some embarrassment...</font>

148
00:08:52,400 --> 00:08:54,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I-I see.</font>

149
00:08:54,550 --> 00:08:56,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, I'm invisible,</font>

150
00:08:56,090 --> 00:08:58,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">so it's not really 
a rational embarrassment.</font>

151
00:08:58,860 --> 00:09:02,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But now I'm catching your embarrassment!</font>

152
00:09:03,510 --> 00:09:04,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm sorry.</font>

153
00:09:04,550 --> 00:09:06,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Do not apologize!</font>

154
00:09:12,630 --> 00:09:14,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">L-Let's have a meal.</font>

155
00:09:14,860 --> 00:09:16,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The hauntings don't start 
until nightfall,</font>

156
00:09:16,930 --> 00:09:18,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">so let's take our time and enjoy!</font>

157
00:09:18,400 --> 00:09:19,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">O-Okay!</font>

158
00:09:23,230 --> 00:09:25,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What was that just now?</font>

159
00:09:32,460 --> 00:09:34,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Was that a paranormal phenomenon?!</font>

160
00:09:34,050 --> 00:09:36,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's surely too soon...</font>

161
00:09:36,560 --> 00:09:39,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm checking it out! 
Wait here, Shizuka-san!</font>

162
00:09:39,640 --> 00:09:41,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">W-Wait!</font>

163
00:09:41,720 --> 00:09:43,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't leave me!</font>

164
00:09:43,900 --> 00:09:45,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">By myself, I'll be...</font>

165
00:09:47,080 --> 00:09:50,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">too scared... please...</font>

166
00:09:52,060 --> 00:09:52,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">All right.</font>

167
00:09:55,540 --> 00:09:58,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll protect you, Shizuka-san.</font>

168
00:09:58,740 --> 00:10:01,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm not scared as long as there's light.</font>

169
00:10:02,480 --> 00:10:04,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I suppose that's not very reassuring.</font>

170
00:10:04,560 --> 00:10:06,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's not true at all!</font>

171
00:10:06,410 --> 00:10:09,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If you don't mind...</font>

172
00:10:09,860 --> 00:10:12,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Could I come with you 
on your investigation?</font>

173
00:10:13,050 --> 00:10:15,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Of course! I'd be happy to have you!</font>

174
00:10:21,200 --> 00:10:22,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">All right. Let's go.</font>

175
00:10:22,800 --> 00:10:23,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Right!</font>

176
00:10:28,180 --> 00:10:30,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, that was fast.</font>

177
00:10:30,150 --> 00:10:31,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Fast?!</font>

178
00:10:31,260 --> 00:10:33,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">There's a mysterious fluid on the floor.</font>

179
00:10:34,030 --> 00:10:35,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Is it blood?!</font>

180
00:10:36,650 --> 00:10:39,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll walk us to where 
I can see it clearly.</font>

181
00:10:48,360 --> 00:10:49,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's black.</font>

182
00:10:49,530 --> 00:10:51,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Black blood?!</font>

183
00:10:54,870 --> 00:10:56,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's rather viscous.</font>

184
00:10:56,770 --> 00:10:58,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Viscous blood?!</font>

185
00:11:00,240 --> 00:11:02,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wait, that smells like...</font>

186
00:11:10,400 --> 00:11:11,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What is it?</font>

187
00:11:11,770 --> 00:11:14,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I saw a person, cut in half, 
floating along.</font>

188
00:11:14,840 --> 00:11:17,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">C-Cut in half?! Floating?!</font>

189
00:11:17,600 --> 00:11:21,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sorry, maybe that 
was too frank a description.</font>

190
00:11:21,250 --> 00:11:23,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No, don't apologize.</font>

191
00:11:24,010 --> 00:11:26,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm not a child.</font>

192
00:11:26,240 --> 00:11:31,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You don't need to mince words 
when giving me information.</font>

193
00:11:31,470 --> 00:11:32,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Shizuka-san...</font>

194
00:11:42,400 --> 00:11:44,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The sound... It's coming closer!</font>

195
00:11:49,700 --> 00:11:52,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I see. The mystery is solved.</font>

196
00:11:54,760 --> 00:11:57,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You've really found the truth?!</font>

197
00:11:57,700 --> 00:11:58,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes.</font>

198
00:11:58,640 --> 00:12:02,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The ocean view from our room 
is what made it all clear.</font>

199
00:12:02,520 --> 00:12:04,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ocean?</font>

200
00:12:04,340 --> 00:12:06,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll get right to the point.</font>

201
00:12:06,680 --> 00:12:10,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The truth behind the paranormal 
phenomena and the haunting...</font>

202
00:12:10,620 --> 00:12:11,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's...</font>

203
00:12:13,010 --> 00:12:14,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">These people!</font>

204
00:12:16,290 --> 00:12:18,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">My employees?!</font>

205
00:12:18,480 --> 00:12:21,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A-Are you playing a prank on me?</font>

206
00:12:22,050 --> 00:12:24,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">C-Certainly not!</font>

207
00:12:24,770 --> 00:12:28,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No, they're just going 
about their jobs normally.</font>

208
00:12:28,470 --> 00:12:33,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But it's so normal to you all, 
you don't perceive it as paranormal.</font>

209
00:12:33,280 --> 00:12:34,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">"Normal"?</font>

210
00:12:34,850 --> 00:12:38,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ma'am, you mentioned the attendant 
was leaving early today.</font>

211
00:12:38,890 --> 00:12:41,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Y-Yes, that's true.</font>

212
00:12:41,430 --> 00:12:44,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">She's had to pull so many 
late nights recently...</font>

213
00:12:45,070 --> 00:12:48,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You were on your way 
home earlier, weren't you?</font>

214
00:12:48,880 --> 00:12:50,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Y-Yes...</font>

215
00:12:50,080 --> 00:12:53,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But I left something behind, 
so I came back to get it...</font>

216
00:12:55,930 --> 00:12:59,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{M}I'll get home early today!</i></font>

217
00:12:59,580 --> 00:13:00,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Huh?</i></font>

218
00:13:01,040 --> 00:13:03,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{M}I forgot my kimono cord!</i></font>

219
00:13:07,300 --> 00:13:10,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{M}So much for getting home early!</i></font>

220
00:13:09,030 --> 00:13:10,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}</i>Achoo!</font>

221
00:13:13,500 --> 00:13:17,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thank goodness I found it.</font>

222
00:13:24,110 --> 00:13:26,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It was the sound of your 
employee moving around.</font>

223
00:13:26,640 --> 00:13:30,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Impossible! All this fuss 
over a few ordinary noises?!</font>

224
00:13:30,850 --> 00:13:33,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The incidents happened mostly at night.</font>

225
00:13:33,340 --> 00:13:36,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And you mentioned she'd 
been pulling late nights...</font>

226
00:13:36,410 --> 00:13:42,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes, when it's late, I'm often in a hurry 
to get the last of my work done...</font>

227
00:13:43,740 --> 00:13:46,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">As for the "bloody" floors,</font>

228
00:13:46,430 --> 00:13:49,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">when I talked to the 
attendant in the hallway...</font>

229
00:13:49,450 --> 00:13:51,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The reviews have been 
complaining about this.</font>

230
00:13:51,720 --> 00:13:53,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm not sure...</font>

231
00:14:01,450 --> 00:14:03,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What's this all about?</font>

232
00:14:03,530 --> 00:14:04,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well...</font>

233
00:14:09,870 --> 00:14:12,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, there I go again!</font>

234
00:14:12,720 --> 00:14:15,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm sorry. I've had a bit of a cold...</font>

235
00:14:16,950 --> 00:14:18,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's his ink.</font>

236
00:14:18,910 --> 00:14:22,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'd thought it smelled familiar!</font>

237
00:14:22,800 --> 00:14:25,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't you have a handkerchief?!</font>

238
00:14:25,510 --> 00:14:27,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Of course I do!</font>

239
00:14:27,700 --> 00:14:29,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But sometimes I don't get to it in time,</font>

240
00:14:29,790 --> 00:14:33,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">or the ones I have get 
all soaked through...</font>

241
00:14:36,630 --> 00:14:42,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And the thing they have in common
is what helped me crack the case.</font>

242
00:14:44,240 --> 00:14:47,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The torso was a rather pallid color.</font>

243
00:14:47,740 --> 00:14:50,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, it could be...</font>

244
00:14:50,230 --> 00:14:51,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You know.</font>

245
00:14:55,140 --> 00:14:56,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hello!</font>

246
00:14:57,110 --> 00:14:58,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I see.</font>

247
00:15:03,140 --> 00:15:04,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hello.</font>

248
00:15:06,280 --> 00:15:09,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This merfolk with a black tail.</font>

249
00:15:09,700 --> 00:15:13,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">S-Something so simple 
caused all this fuss?</font>

250
00:15:13,230 --> 00:15:15,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What they have in common 
is being on the night shift.</font>

251
00:15:15,580 --> 00:15:19,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">When customers run into them at night 
when there's no one around,</font>

252
00:15:19,020 --> 00:15:22,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">they likely get scared 
and lock themselves in their rooms.</font>

253
00:15:24,180 --> 00:15:27,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">By the time they come out, 
the ink has already been cleaned up,</font>

254
00:15:27,460 --> 00:15:29,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and there's no one to be seen or heard.</font>

255
00:15:29,520 --> 00:15:36,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">S-So we were scaring the customers 
just by going about our business?</font>

256
00:15:36,740 --> 00:15:41,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Your inn is by the sea, 
so a lot of aquatic races work here.</font>

257
00:15:41,520 --> 00:15:43,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">These things are normal for all of you,</font>

258
00:15:43,330 --> 00:15:46,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">but tourists haven't seen 
anything like it before.</font>

259
00:15:46,860 --> 00:15:49,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So they assumed it was paranormal.</font>

260
00:15:49,580 --> 00:15:53,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And that explains why we didn't notice!</font>

261
00:15:53,180 --> 00:15:56,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I never thought that 
the sounds that were normal</font>

262
00:15:56,520 --> 00:15:59,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">to us would seem eerie to other races...</font>

263
00:15:59,360 --> 00:16:03,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I've slipped on the squid ink 
before myself...</font>

264
00:16:03,890 --> 00:16:06,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But I always wipe it up right away!</font>

265
00:16:08,090 --> 00:16:09,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Achoo!</font>

266
00:16:10,990 --> 00:16:11,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm soaked.</font>

267
00:16:12,280 --> 00:16:14,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, now that we know the cause,</font>

268
00:16:14,640 --> 00:16:18,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">we can discuss tomorrow how to deal 
with it all, including reviews.</font>

269
00:16:18,870 --> 00:16:21,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Of course! Thank you so much!</font>

270
00:16:24,400 --> 00:16:26,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It feels great to solve the mystery!</font>

271
00:16:26,840 --> 00:16:29,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm sorry we had to put off our meal.</font>

272
00:16:30,200 --> 00:16:33,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But the food here is so delicious!</font>

273
00:16:33,370 --> 00:16:34,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes.</font>

274
00:16:36,740 --> 00:16:39,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The baths here are amazing, too!</font>

275
00:16:39,230 --> 00:16:41,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I hope things turn around for them!</font>

276
00:16:41,360 --> 00:16:42,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Indeed.</font>

277
00:16:43,030 --> 00:16:47,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And now that the case is behind us, 
we can have a good night's sleep.</font>

278
00:16:48,030 --> 00:16:50,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're going right to sleep?</font>

279
00:16:52,580 --> 00:16:55,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You were incredible today, Akira-san.</font>

280
00:16:57,280 --> 00:17:00,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I want you to kiss me.</font>

281
00:17:04,550 --> 00:17:06,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We have an early day tomorrow.</font>

282
00:17:06,780 --> 00:17:07,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let's get to bed.</font>

283
00:17:08,800 --> 00:17:09,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Right.</font>

284
00:17:10,480 --> 00:17:11,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Good night.</font>

285
00:17:13,510 --> 00:17:14,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Good night...</font>

286
00:17:23,220 --> 00:17:24,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Akira-san...</font>

287
00:17:24,630 --> 00:17:27,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's possible this is 
just my imagination, but...</font>

288
00:17:27,050 --> 00:17:30,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sometimes, it feels like 
something's holding you back.</font>

289
00:17:31,920 --> 00:17:36,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">W-Well, but it has been a long day.</font>

290
00:17:36,070 --> 00:17:38,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I know you're tired. Sorry.</font>

291
00:17:42,720 --> 00:17:47,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{M}Maybe Akira-san's just not 
big on physical affection.</i></font>

292
00:17:48,000 --> 00:17:49,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{M}There are people like that.</i></font>

293
00:17:51,910 --> 00:17:56,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{M}Wait, maybe I'm just 
not visually attractive?</i></font>

294
00:17:57,050 --> 00:18:00,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{M}I don't know what that's like 
for people who can see,</i></font>

295
00:18:00,880 --> 00:18:03,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>but I've heard that it's a factor...</i></font>

296
00:18:04,230 --> 00:18:08,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{M}I get it. I'm ugly!</i></font>

297
00:18:08,450 --> 00:18:11,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{M}I've never really thought 
about my face before...</i></font>

298
00:18:11,950 --> 00:18:14,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{M}What a shocking truth 
to have to face now...</i></font>

299
00:18:14,820 --> 00:18:17,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm sorry I'm ugly.</font>

300
00:18:17,610 --> 00:18:18,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Where did that come from?!</font>

301
00:18:18,900 --> 00:18:22,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You won't canoodle with me!</font>

302
00:18:22,060 --> 00:18:24,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Seriously, where 
are you getting this from?!</font>

303
00:18:24,120 --> 00:18:28,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I get it. It's hard to admit to.</font>

304
00:18:31,250 --> 00:18:33,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">All right. Let's talk this out.</font>

305
00:18:34,280 --> 00:18:35,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's just...</font>

306
00:18:35,200 --> 00:18:37,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll have to talk 
about my last girlfriend,</font>

307
00:18:37,940 --> 00:18:40,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">so it might make you uncomfortable.</font>

308
00:18:40,720 --> 00:18:42,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Do you still want to do it?</font>

309
00:18:43,470 --> 00:18:44,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes.</font>

310
00:18:45,370 --> 00:18:49,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">At my last job... when I was 
working at a big detective agency,</font>

311
00:18:50,040 --> 00:18:52,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I was in an interspecies romance.</font>

312
00:18:52,690 --> 00:18:56,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">She tried hard to understand me 
as an invisible person,</font>

313
00:18:56,790 --> 00:19:00,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and I tried hard to understand her, too.</font>

314
00:19:00,670 --> 00:19:06,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I felt like there was a time when we 
both really trusted each other, too.</font>

315
00:19:15,120 --> 00:19:18,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But, one night, it was like 
she couldn't bear it anymore...</font>

316
00:19:22,930 --> 00:19:26,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Or rather, I suppose it took 
a lot of courage to say...</font>

317
00:19:26,910 --> 00:19:28,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">that I frightened her.</font>

318
00:19:29,070 --> 00:19:34,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">She couldn't help but feel afraid of 
being touched by someone she couldn't see.</font>

319
00:19:35,070 --> 00:19:39,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Just being who I am triggered 
an instinctive fear in my partner.</font>

320
00:19:39,430 --> 00:19:42,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">She always looked so happy...</font>

321
00:19:43,280 --> 00:19:47,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But I think she was just 
trying not to hurt me.</font>

322
00:19:47,880 --> 00:19:49,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I felt like I'd done 
something awful to her.</font>

323
00:20:01,310 --> 00:20:03,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Er... What was that?</font>

324
00:20:09,000 --> 00:20:11,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Where's that mouth of yours now?</font>

325
00:20:11,970 --> 00:20:13,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Shizuka-san?</font>

326
00:20:14,960 --> 00:20:16,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Is this it?</font>

327
00:20:20,280 --> 00:20:22,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's my right cheek.</font>

328
00:20:23,000 --> 00:20:24,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Got it.</font>

329
00:20:26,210 --> 00:20:27,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's my nose.</font>

330
00:20:27,600 --> 00:20:28,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Then...</font>

331
00:20:32,310 --> 00:20:33,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">My upper lip.</font>

332
00:20:34,120 --> 00:20:37,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Is that full credit? Half credit?</font>

333
00:20:37,630 --> 00:20:39,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let's say full credit.</font>

334
00:20:46,610 --> 00:20:47,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">My eyelid.</font>

335
00:20:51,830 --> 00:20:53,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It was a little wet.</font>

336
00:20:53,520 --> 00:20:54,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How insensitive.</font>

337
00:21:04,600 --> 00:21:07,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Would you like to spend 
the night like this?</font>

338
00:21:09,660 --> 00:21:11,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Y-Yes!</font>

339
00:21:11,570 --> 00:21:14,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If you'll get off me for a minute, 
I'll pull the cover over us.</font>

340
00:21:14,550 --> 00:21:18,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Aw, I thought we could 
stay like this awhile!</font>

341
00:21:18,580 --> 00:21:20,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You'll catch a cold.</font>

342
00:21:20,740 --> 00:21:22,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Get your yukata back on straight, too.</font>

343
00:21:23,160 --> 00:21:27,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I don't know how to fix it. 
You'll have to do it!</font>

344
00:21:27,160 --> 00:21:28,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Of course.</font>

345
00:21:33,190 --> 00:21:34,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're enjoying yourself.</font>

346
00:21:36,520 --> 00:21:38,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I can smell you.</font>

347
00:21:39,610 --> 00:21:41,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I love this smell!</font>

348
00:21:41,330 --> 00:21:47,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You know, you've never 
actually told me you love me.</font>

349
00:21:47,700 --> 00:21:49,000
